                        Usually it takes 1 to 2 days! Please be patient
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Would you like to Shop from <span style="color:limegreen;">ProGamers</span> Store <span>
                            <a href="@Url.Action("Index","Ecommerce")">
                                <i class="fa fa-home fa-2x"></i>
